    <item>
      <title>先锋创纪录的降费举措令竞争对手贝莱德和景顺陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/vanguard-s-record-fee-cuts-tighten-screws-on-blackrock-invesco</link>
      <description><![CDATA[先锋集团 (Vanguard Group Inc.) 为降低投资大众的费用而采取的迄今为止最大的举措，让行业竞争对手面临一个痛苦的选择。要么效仿，可能损失数亿美元收入 — — 要么坚守阵地，冒着失去急需的市场份额的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/vanguard-s-record-fee-cuts-tighten-screws-on-blackrock-invesco</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:46:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
